Following his announcement to release a song that captures the ongoing s3xual scandal involving Apostle suleman and some celebrities, Uche Maduwagwu has challenged female colleagues whose names were listed to deny the allegation before Sango and Amadioha (Yoruba and Igbo names God of thunder respectively). Since the news went viral of Suleman’s alleged involvement with many top female celebrities from Nollywood and BBNaija, some of them, including the cleric have denied the claim. But Maduagwu dared the mentioned actresses to prove their innocence beyond their keypad in the shrine before Sango or Amadioha.   Peter Olayinka dedicates match victory to new baby     I’m super proud of Fireboy DML, Rema – Olamide     Offset hints on collaboration with Burna Boy   According to the controversial media personality, his proposal is solely meant as an experiment to find out if the gods would respond to the denial with thunder ‘shapeless like Aunty Ble Ble Ikebe’. He said: “I challenge all the popular actresses Gistlover claim dated Apostle to come forward before Sango or Amadioha to repeat their denial. I just want to see an Experiment.” “We are not saying you did it. This is just for experiment sake. “U fit even do Live video at the shrine. We just want to see if the gods go reply with thunder wey dey shapeless like Aunty Ble Ble Ikebe.”